meta.title: What did I learn this week (2022) - 01
meta.description: Weekly summarization and review of things I've learned in the first week of January 2022

pageProps.content:
• Someone logged his life for 10 years.
  • Found a compilation of best things and stuffs of 2021.
  • Prince of persia game is available in web browser.
  • Found a modern guide to OAuth.
  • RSS Bridge - RSS feed for websites missing it.
